    <note>Lian(3) Hengfu [7286] Xiang(2) Zhuanfan's [7238] son-in-law. He held minor fiscal offices in 1075-1076. He is probably related to the other Jianning Lian(3), e.g. Ding (jinshi in 1963, but not in dataset)), Hui (jinshi in 1109, but not in dataset) and the Jianan jinshi in 1148 and 1256. He is certainly related to Yifu [20086], who earned the degree in 1076 and who is identified as a Jianan resident. Fujian TZ, 147.26a; XCB, 267.2b, 268.1a, 278.4b. CBD, 5, 3839.</note>
